Another incredible Christmas in Calgary 🇨🇦🎄🎅🏻

It might have been the coldest winter in Calgary since 1884, but with all the love, laughter, little kiddos, dogs, family, and wine, we felt warm and cozy. 

I hope your Christmas was full of love & light. ❤️

I was feeling anxious about writing some long-winded reflective post about 2022, but all I have to say is that this year had many ups and downs, but overall I learned some of the most valuable life lessons. 

Everything happens for a reason! (Cliché, I know, but it’s so true!) With a positive forward-focused mindset and the right people in your bubble, you will overcome any challenge and come out stronger and wiser. 

Cheers to my people 💓Thank you for dancing through life with me. I love you so much. 

Put a 👍🏻 in the comments if you agree that 2023 is going to be a GREAT year!

Thrilled to announce my role as Head of Events & Community for Leverage and The Optimize Group! 

Life’s magic unfolds when you say yes, follow your intuition, and embrace new opportunities. 

Working alongside @nicholassonnenberg , our mission is to help high-level entrepreneurs, thought leaders, and executives optimize both their business and personal life by uniting in luxurious settings.

We’re redefining the business mastermind with immersive events in 5-star locations, offering curated connections, diverse perspectives, collaborative problem-solving, and unique opportunities. 

Join us on this transformative journey! ✨
